product__vendor.liquid
  desc: <p>TKO Strength &amp; Performance was founded in 1996 by Garry Kurtz. TKO was first a boxing equipment company (hence the name Technical KnockOut), but has since evolved into a health and fitness equipment manufacturing company.</p><p>TKO now offers a variety of products, from boxing gloves to yoga mats, or from dumbbells to functional trainers and cardio equipment such as elliptical machines and indoor bikes.</p><br>
